cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper proposes a method for temporal action proposal generation in videos using visual features and position embedding information. This task falls under computer vision and machine learning, which are covered by the arXiv sub-categories cs.CV and cs.LG. The method also involves segment proposal generation and actionness evaluation, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on public datasets, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
